CFP: 12,6-11,2; PL: 12,09-11,7; PLB: 3,30-2,75; FF: 2,9-2,1; FL: 4,8-4,6; MFL: 3-2,6; MTL: 3,1-2,7; HL: 6,63-5,85; HW: 1,9-1,4; HL: 5,8-5,2.
</paragraph>
